{"tid":1241000,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實去到呢一刻 大家首要做既係清算警隊同埋幫義士","createTime":"2019-06-18T14:08:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-18T14:57:35.000Z","uid":93350,"like":33,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"8a14c19209a3c668b64d582c211fe050794f35c9","tid":1241000,"uid":93350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T14:08:57.000Z","msg":"我相信而家777短期內都唔會夠膽再推逃犯條例<br />\n大家而家應該集中火力去追究黑警 同埋諗下方法點樣去幫義士<br />\n<br />\n好老實講6.16號200萬大遊行 <br />\n好多人出黎遊行既主要原因都係因為班狗6.12亂鳩咁黎(包括我自己同身邊D朋友都係)<br />\n<br />\n頭先係格離POST見到有巴打話要係立會到用特權法追究班黑警<br />\n要用而家既民意去令建制投讚成票 我覺得呢個方法係有效<br />\n始終監警會大家都知道係完全無撚用架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n傳送門:<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1240711/page/2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1240711/page/2</a>"},{"pid":"d943212f2f4884c77ec19991bcded74c98b1a858","tid":1241000,"uid":93350,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T14:09:35.000Z","msg":"大家醒下 唔好將義士用完即棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb601598643df42e0aedf9e16a817ad85d7ee4ac","tid":1241000,"uid":93350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T14:09:57.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"d6dbe66b0ea187d9013c149b487421d8c662e531","tid":1241000,"uid":93350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T14:10:12.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"224aafc20b86e90307cd4233d7f26d88bd91c940","tid":1241000,"uid":93350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T14:10:22.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"55997c82c5fad1c37efc236bd1e7fa62abe5cb80","tid":1241000,"uid":223506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T14:11:05.000Z","msg":"岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"915a937f024b64e2e3aecf432dd2856650494b98","tid":1241000,"uid":93350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cited